{"tid":1514110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天晴有藍絲日日屌老母 啱啱仲整喊左個女手足","createTime":"2019-08-28T15:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T15:14:42.000Z","uid":308710,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee7b28ef6d449986d807353d8e137901f75d44f","tid":1514110,"uid":308710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭車返到屋企 見到樓下有個呀叔係到屌緊<br />\n<br />\n「日日嘈撚住晒 唔洗瞓呀 嗌乜撚嘢呀<br />\n夠膽落嚟嗌囉 又唔夠膽落嚟 好撚型呀以家」<br />\n<br />\n跟住有個女手足本身就係樓下公園到嗌<br />\n個呀叔屌屌下行左去個女手足前面屌佢<br />\n我即刻趕過去 但無奈我都仲細個唔夠膽反屌佢<br />\n比左張紙巾個女手足 講左幾句就走左<br />\n<br />\n有冇住天晴嘅手足聽日可以落去一齊屌返個藍絲呀叔<br />\n懷疑日日係到屌老母嗰個就係佢<br />\n樓上有個巴打都有反屌佢 做得好！"},{"pid":"dfed8d04845a9ee1951b97cd597822cc34ff3b5e","tid":1514110,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"９月２日 - 開學日<br />\n<br />\n番母校幫學妹學弟打打氣！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開學日早會大嗌光復香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dLnbES\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dLnbES</a>"},{"pid":"a4dc076cc1ea4f8e22b0dfca422bd64519554410","tid":1514110,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fc6960e93ccb79955c34d1f74cffb6d7744fd9","tid":1514110,"uid":295662,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"女手足冇人陪唔好自己落去嗌呀<br />\nD阿伯無性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d52e6990dd7f804cdf0ea0d7c830a80d5d15bcc","tid":1514110,"uid":307128,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"聽日留下見😊希望阿叔佢仲係到啦"},{"pid":"505f712dc73bff7d197475e6a2d6762b0f4f37be","tid":1514110,"uid":33927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91fc6960e93ccb79955c34d1f74cffb6d7744fd9","tid":1514110,"uid":295662,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"女手足冇人陪唔好自己落去嗌呀<br /